<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/137.0.0.0 Safari/537.36" version="27.1.6" scale="1" border="0"> <diagram name="Page-1" id="hdS8Fb_V-9kqf6li_edK"> <mxGraphModel dx="3848" dy="1143" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0"> <root> <mxCell id="0" /> <mxCell id="1" parent="0" /> <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{"data":"@startuml Tower Defense - Diagramme de Séquence : Tir avec Effet de Feu

!theme plain
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam maxmessagesize 60

title Séquence de Tir avec Application d'Effet de Feu

actor \"Game Loop\" as Game
participant \"CannonScript\" as Cannon
participant \"EnemyManagerScript\" as EnemyMgr
participant \"Pool\" as Pool
participant \"BulletScript\" as Bullet
participant \"FireEffect\" as FireEff
participant \"FireBulletVisualDecorator\" as FireDeco
participant \"EnemyScript\" as Enemy
participant \"BurnedState\" as BurnState
participant \"GameManager\" as GameMgr

== Phase de Détection ==
Game -> Cannon : FixedUpdate()
activate Cannon

Cannon -> EnemyMgr : GetEnemyInRange(position, range, tags)
activate EnemyMgr
EnemyMgr --> Cannon : enemy
deactivate EnemyMgr

alt Ennemi trouvé ET cooldown écoulé
 
 == Phase de Création du Projectile ==
 Cannon -> Pool : ActivateObject(\"bullet\")
 activate Pool
 Pool --> Cannon : bulletGameObject
 deactivate Pool
 
 Cannon -> Bullet : Configurer propriétés
 note right: Speed, Range, Damage, Direction, Target
 
 == Phase d'Application des Patterns ==
 Cannon -> Bullet : ProjectileEffect = new FireEffect()
 Cannon -> Bullet : BulletVisualDecorator = new FireBulletVisualDecorator()
 
 Cannon -> Bullet : Init()
 activate Bullet
 
 Bullet -> FireDeco : ApplyVisual(this)
 activate FireDeco
 FireDeco -> Bullet : Changer couleur en rouge
 deactivate FireDeco
 
 Bullet -> Bullet : SetActive(true)
 deactivate Bullet
 
 == Phase de Collision ==
 note over Bullet : Le projectile se déplace...
 
 Bullet -> Enemy : OnTriggerEnter2D()
 activate Enemy
 
 Bullet -> FireEff : ApplyEffect(enemy, bullet)
 activate FireEff
 
 FireEff -> Enemy : TakeDamage(bullet.Damage)
 FireEff -> Enemy : ApplyBurn(duration=2.0f, damagePerSecond=0.4f)
 
 deactivate FireEff
 
 == Phase de Changement d'État ==
 Enemy -> BurnState : new BurnedState(burnDamage, previousState)
 activate BurnState
 
 Enemy -> Enemy : ChangeState(burnedState)
 Enemy -> BurnState : Enter(this)
 
 BurnState -> Enemy : SetColorByEffect(Fire)
 note right: Ennemi devient rouge
 
 deactivate BurnState
 deactivate Enemy
 
 == Phase de Nettoyage ==
 Bullet -> Pool : DeactivateObject(this)
 activate Pool
 Pool -> Bullet : SetActive(false)
 deactivate Pool
 
 == Phase de Récompense (si ennemi mort) ==
 alt Ennemi mort
 Enemy -> GameMgr : EnemyKilled(this)
 activate GameMgr
 GameMgr -> GameMgr : AddMoney(enemy.Money)
 deactivate GameMgr
 
 Enemy -> Pool : SpawnCoins()
 end
 
end

deactivate Cannon
